Class SeaGlassIcon

      com.seaglasslookandfeel.component.SeaGlassIcon
All Implemented Interfaces:
Icon
public class SeaGlassIcon
extends sun.swing.plaf.synth.SynthIcon

An icon that delegates to a painter.

Based on NimbusIcon by Richard Bair. Reimplemented because too much is package local.

See Also:
NimbusIcon

paintIcon

public void paintIcon(Component c,
                      Graphics g,
                      int x,
                      int y)
Implements the standard Icon interface's paintIcon method as the standard synth stub passes null for the context and this will cause us to not paint any thing, so we override here so that we can paint the enabled state if no synth context is available

Specified by:
paintIcon in interface Icon
Overrides:
paintIcon in class sun.swing.plaf.synth.SynthIcon
Parameters:
c - the component to paint.
g - the Graphics context to paint with.
x - the x coordinate of the upper-left corner of the icon.
y - the y coordinate of the upper-left corner of the icon.
